docs.abstract: A defamation lawsuit may expose the creators of the account, called Diet Madison Avenue, that published the names of alleged harassers in the ad industry.
docs.snippet: A defamation lawsuit may expose the creators of the account, called Diet Madison Avenue, that published the names of alleged harassers in the ad industry.
docs.lead_paragraph: Since October, advertisers have been riveted by an anonymous Instagram account called Diet Madison Avenue, which solicited reports of sexual misconduct in the ad industry and published the names of alleged harassers. But now, the account has been deleted and its creators’ names could be made public through a defamation lawsuit brought by a man who claims Diet Madison Avenue posted false allegations about him that cost him his job.

headline.main: Instagram Account That Sought Harassment Tales May Be Unmasked

docs.abstract: Is a stranger being rude? Your seat mate crying? A friend acting strangely? We’re all dealing with something, as our Sketch Guy columnist reminds us.

docs.lead_paragraph: I was in the airport when I found out that the mother of one of my best friends had just died quite suddenly. She was at dinner with a friend, felt sick and was dead within a few hours.

headline.main: Ask Yourself This: What Burdens Is That Other Person Carrying?

docs.abstract: Much of the internet feels terrible. But using the web to learn an offline hobby can give you a glimpse of a healthier relationship with your digital devices.
docs.snippet: Much of the internet feels terrible. But using the web to learn an offline hobby can give you a glimpse of a healthier relationship with your digital devices.
docs.lead_paragraph: Pottery, improbably, is the latest escapist pastime to sweep the nation. Because making ceramics requires persistence and all-consuming concentration, it is said to be a perfect salve for a particular set of modern anxieties — too much work, too much news, too much internet. When your hands are slathered in clay, you cannot fiddle around with your phone.

headline.main: How Online Hobbyists Can Reaffirm Your Faith in the Internet
headline.print_headline: Lost Faith in the Web? Restore It, With a Hobby
